headline: CME Group to Launch FX Tape+ to Provide Centralized Reference Prices for the FX Market
summary: CME Group, the world's leading derivatives marketplace, today announced that it will launch CME FX Tape+ to provide centralized reference prices and a comprehensive view of FX market liquidity from its transparent central limit order book (CLOB) marketplaces, including FX futures, EBS Market, FX Spot+‌ and FX Link. FX Tape+ is set to launch later this year.
